WEBVTT

00:00:00.916 --> 00:00:04.356
"How many times must a man look up

00:00:04.356 --> 00:00:07.036
Before he can see the sky?"

00:00:07.956 --> 00:00:12.116
That's a quote from
a famous song by Bob Dylan.

00:00:12.876 --> 00:00:15.796
I love that line because it reminds me

00:00:15.836 --> 00:00:21.236
that sometimes what we need is actually
right there in front of us.

00:00:22.076 --> 00:00:25.516
I will argue that that is also the case
with climate change.

00:00:26.276 --> 00:00:30.756
We can actually replace some
of the biggest sources of the problem,